Ian Walters allegedly killed his wife Tracy by deliberately driving his truck into a tree at 84mph . 
  He denies murder of his wife who died two days after the crash near Markfield, Leicestershire . 
  Prosecutors allege he deliberately steered his Mitsubishi L200 off the M1 after his wife said she wanted a divorce and made allegations of domestic abuse . 
  Two dogs and suitcases were thrown out of the pick-up truck as it hit trees . 
  Leicester Crown Court was told that Tracy Walters died after making a flurry of calls to police about sex-obsessed husband . 
  Walters was driving the truck at the time of the crash . 
 